# --- Sphinx / sphinx-gallery build output ---
# This repo only needs the translation memory (*.po) and the gettext
# source text (*.rst). Everything below is regenerated by `make html`
# on every CI run and must never be committed (it caused ~300 MB of
# binary history bloat).
*.doctree
*.pickle
*.vtksz
*.vtk
*.zip
*.png
*.gif
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.ipynb
*.md5
*.codeobj.json
locale/jupyter_execute/*
locale/pot/*
locale/.doctrees/*
tx
